>> +                    polarity
>> +                );
>> +                Polarity::Normal
> Either Polarity::Normal is the correct thing to return in such a case, but then
> we do not need the pr_warn!(), or it is not, but then this should be a TryFrom
> impl instead.
>
>> +            }
>> +        }
>> +    }
>> +}
